Parameters:
atomicNumber - The atomic number of the element
symbol - The chemical symbol of the element
html - An HTML symbol for the element
name - The name of the element
atomicWeight - The atomic weight of the element
melt - The melting point of the element (degrees Kelvin)
boil - The boiling point of the element (degrees Kelvin)
density - The density of the element
abunde - Element abundance data
abunds - Element abundance data
rea - The reactivity of the element
maxIpp - The max allowed inspired partial pressure for this element for a habitable planet
